high_descs: Turn and go to the trash can to the right of the sink.
Pick up the empty roll of toilet paper tube that is in the trash can.
With the empty roll of toilet paper tube turn and go to the black table in front of the tub with the plant on it.
Place the empty roll of toilet paper tube in front of the plant on the table.
Turn and go to the roll of toilet paper that is hanging on the wall next to the toilet.
Grab the roll of toilet paper that is hanging on the wall next to the toilet.
With the roll of toilet paper in hand turn and go to the black table in front of the tub with the plant on it.
Place the roll of toilet paper to the left of the candle that is in the front.
anns.task_desc: Move toilet paper and empty roll to black table.

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the trash can.
Pick up the empty roll in the trash can.
Turn around and step forward to face the black table.
Place the empty roll on the black table.
Turn left and step forward to face the toilet paper on the wall.
Remove the toilet paper from the holder on the wall.
Turn right and step forward to face the black table.
Place the toilet paper on the black table.
anns.task_desc: To put a roll of toilet paper plus an empty roll on the black table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the trash can
Grab the cardboard tube out of the trash can
Turn around and go to the end table
Put the cardboard on the table
Turn around and go to the toilet paper on the wall
Grab the toilet paper roll off of the wall
Turn around and go to the end table
Put the toilet paper on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a cardboard tube and a toilet paper roll on an end table
